OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1776363050
OL,3,CAppeal after teenager goes missing
OL,4,Cwith puppy
OL,6,FPolice are appealing for help to find
OL,7,Fa teenager who has gone missing with
OL,8,Fher puppy.
OL,10,FThe 15-year-old, from Northallerton,
OL,11,Fnamed only as "Ellie" by North
OL,12,FYorkshire Police, was last seen on
OL,13,FCCTV at Darlington Railway Station at
OL,14,F1.15pm on Wednesday, 15 April.
OL,16,FA police spokesperson said: "Her
OL,17,Ffamily have been unable to contact her
OL,18,Fever since and we're growing
OL,19,Fincreasingly concerned for her
OL,20,Fwelfare."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/3
