OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1776363050
OL,3,CAppeal after teenager goes missing
OL,4,Cwith puppy
OL,6,FEllie is 5ft 3ins tall and slim, with
OL,7,Fshoulder-length, straight blonde hair.
OL,9,FShe was last seen wearing grey joggers
OL,10,Fand a white top and had a black
OL,11,Fhandbag and was carrying her black
OL,12,FPatterdale terrier puppy.
OL,14,FEllie has links to Darlington and
OL,15,FNorthallerton.
